    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "1998 sedan with 210,000 miles. The vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and transmission are operational, though the car shows significant wear and tear consistent with its age and high mileage. Maintenance is up to date, but cosmetic imperfections are present both inside and out.",
